                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#108r">108r</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወሐ፡ በቶ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡
