                              ሰማያት፡ በ፵ብር፡ የተገዛ፡ ከመ፡ ይኵና፡ መድሐኒተ፡ ነብስ፡ ወስጋ፡ ምልእተ፡ ጸጋ፡ ወግርማ፡ እምመሰገርተ፡
                              አ{ር}ዌ፡ መስጤማ፡ ያድኅና፡ እም፡ ሕማመ፡ ስጋ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ትከ፡ ለወለተ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ለዓለም፡ ወለዓለም፡
                              አሜን፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#108r">108r</locus>: This is the book which Walatta
                              Samāʿt donated to the tabot of St Michael of Nǝhǝb, in the year of
                              Luke,  (when) our King is Mǝnǝlik, so that it might be for her the
                              guide to the Kingdom of Heaven. It was bought for 40 Bǝrr so that it
                              might be for her the solvation of soul and body, full of grace and
                              majesty; it might save her from the deceits  of Mastema, so that is
                              might save her from the malady of flesh, for eternity might it be (?)
                              for Walatta Samāʿt, for eternity. Amen, amen and amen.</quote>
                           <note> Mention of King Mǝnǝlik (Mǝnilǝk) II (r. 1889-1913). </note>
                        </item>
